claim.claim-text:
A thermoplastic resin composition comprising:
a polycarbonate resin;
a large-diameter rubber polymer having an average particle diameter of about 500 nm to about 3,000 nm;
an aromatic vinyl copolymer resin;
a core-shell graft copolymer; and
a phosphorus flame retardant,
wherein the core-shell graft copolymer is obtained through graft polymerization of an epoxy group-containing acrylate monomer for a shell to a core formed of a silicone-based rubber polymer having an average particle diameter of about 100 nm to about 300 nm.
